imageDescription: A simple image that represents the song could be a silhouette of a girl standing on a pile of broken glass, surrounded by a dreamy night sky filled with stars. In the background, there are colorful swirls representing the chaos and madness of the world. The image captures the vulnerability and strength of the girl, as well as the juxtaposition between nighttime and daytime dreamers.
